author: The Critical Drinker
description:
It should have been a musical triumph. A capable director, an all-star cast that includes Judi Dench, Ian McKellen, Idris Elba and Taylor Swift, and a massively popular IP. And yet, Cats became one of the biggest cinematic disasters in Hollywood history. Find out how this calamity came to be with another episode of Production Hell.

author: The Critical Drinker
description:
Join us for Open Bar 166 where Chris Gore will give us his early review of Avatar Fire And Ash, we'll discuss whether Stranger Things Season 5 lives up to the hype, and whether Marvel has abandoned the M-She-U and decided they'd like to start making money again. Myself, MauLer, Film Threat, Little Platoon and Random Film Talk will be on hand to answer your questions.
